      <Nickname>AM 'Barlow'</Nickname>
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;) - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_HEIMPACT</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-11 AM 'Barlow'&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 1 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-1 body, which is a nimble general-purpose missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using a Passive Wake seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

$MISSILESTAT_PRIMARYSEEKER: $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_CAPS (&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;)

$MISSILESTAT_SPEED: 250 $UNIT_METERSPERSEC
$MISSILESTAT_DISTANCE: 5 000 $UNIT_METERS
$MISSILESTAT_TOPSPEEDTIME: 0,6 $UNIT_SECONDS
$MISSILESTAT_TURNRATE: 5,7 $UNIT_GS
